Package: officerWinTools
Title: Functions to Compliment 'officer' package in a Windows environment 
Version: 0.1.0
Imports:
    officer, 
    R.utils
Suggests:
    dplyr
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Joshua",
           family = "Mire",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "the.doctor@joshmire.com")
Description: THIS PACKAGE REQUIRES A WINDOWS OPERATING SYSTEM AND MICROSOFT 
    OFFICE.  The package is meant to be used along side the 'officer' package.  
    The package includes functions for exporting Microsoft Word and PowerPoint 
    files a .pdf files.  The package also includes a function for updating the 
    tables of contents of a Microsoft Word document created with 'officer'.
